**Potential coalitions:**

United Left Coalition (<span style="color: #E3000F;">**SPD**</span> + <span style="color: #8B0000;">**KPD**</span>): [+ united_left_coalition_thuringia +]%

Grand Coalition (<span style="color: var(--nlp-color);">**[+ nlp_name +]**</span> + <span style="color: #E3000F;">**SPD**</span> + <span style="color: var(--fvp-color);">**[+ fvp_name +]**</span> + <span style="color: #000000;">**Z**</span>): [+ grand_coalition_thuringia +]%

Bourgeois Coalition (<span style="color: var(--nlp-color);">**[+ nlp_name +]**</span>[? if not rdp_formed: + <span style="color: var(--fvp-color);">**[+ fvp_name +]**</span> ?][? if wp_exist: + <span style="color: #B8996F;">**WP**</span> ?][? if rlb_exist: + <span style="color: #209E00;">**ThLB**</span> ?][? if csvd_exist: + <span style="color: #1DB4E1;">**CSVD**</span> ?]+ <span style="color: #000000;">**Z**</span>): [+ bourgeois_coalition_thuringia +]%

Right Coalition (<span style="color: var(--nlp-color);">**[+ nlp_name +]**</span> + <span style="color: #3F7BC1;">**DNVP**</span> [? if kvp_exist: + <span style="color: #455B95;">**KVP**</span> ?][? if kswr_exist: + <span style="color: #003755;">**KSWR**</span> ?][? if wp_exist: + <span style="color: #B8996F;">**WP**</span> ?][? if rlb_exist: + <span style="color: #209E00;">**ThLB**</span> ?][? if csvd_exist: + <span style="color: #1DB4E1;">**CSVD**</span> ?]+ <span style="color: #000000;">**Z**</span>): [+ right_coalition_thuringia +]%

There are some potential coalition arrangements.

@thuringia_coalition_menu

- @united_left_coalition_thuringia
- @grand_coalition_thuringia
- @bourgeois_coalition_thuringia
- @right_coalition_thuringia
- @no_majority_thuringia




@united_left_coalition_thuringia
title: The Social Democrats form a coalition with the <span style="color: #8B0000;">**KPD**</span>!
subtitle: <span style="color: #E3000F;">**SPD**</span> + <span style="color: #8B0000;">**KPD**</span> ([+ united_left_coalition_thuringia +]%)
view-if: united_left_coalition_thuringia > 50 and year != 1922
on-arrival: in_united_left_coalition_thuringia = 1;
go-to: mp

WIP


@grand_coalition_thuringia
title: We can form a Grand Coalition.
subtitle: <span style="color: var(--nlp-color);">**[+ nlp_name +]**</span> + <span style="color: #E3000F;">**SPD**</span> + <span style="color: var(--fvp-color);">**[+ fvp_name +]**</span> + <span style="color: #000000;">**Z**</span> ([+ grand_coalition_thuringia +]%)
view-if: grand_coalition_thuringia > 50
choose-if: year != 1922
unavailable-subtitle: The <span style="color: #E3000F;">**SPD**</span> doesn't want to form a coalition with us.
on-arrival: in_grand_coalition_thuringia = 1; nlp_thuringia = 1;
go-to: mp

WIP


@bourgeois_coalition_thuringia
title: We can form a Bourgeois Coalition.
subtitle: <span style="color: var(--nlp-color);">**[+ nlp_name +]**</span>[? if not rdp_formed: + <span style="color: var(--fvp-color);">**[+ fvp_name +]**</span> ?][? if wp_exist: + <span style="color: #B8996F;">**WP**</span> ?][? if rlb_exist: + <span style="color: #209E00;">**ThLB**</span> ?][? if csvd_exist: + <span style="color: #1DB4E1;">**CSVD**</span> ?]+ <span style="color: #000000;">**Z**</span> ([+ bourgeois_coalition_thuringia +]%)
view-if: bourgeois_coalition_thuringia > 50
on-arrival: in_bourgeois_coalition_thuringia = 1; nlp_thuringia = 1;
go-to: mp

WIP


@right_coalition_thuringia
title: We can form a Right Coalition.
subtitle: <span style="color: var(--nlp-color);">**[+ nlp_name +]**</span> + <span style="color: #3F7BC1;">**DNVP**</span> [? if kvp_exist: + <span style="color: #455B95;">**KVP**</span> ?][? if kswr_exist: + <span style="color: #003755;">**KSWR**</span> ?][? if wp_exist: + <span style="color: #B8996F;">**WP**</span> ?][? if rlb_exist: + <span style="color: #209E00;">**ThLB**</span> ?][? if csvd_exist: + <span style="color: #1DB4E1;">**CSVD**</span> ?]+ <span style="color: #000000;">**Z**</span> ([+ right_coalition_thuringia +]%)
view-if: right_coalition_thuringia > 50
on-arrival: in_right_coalition_thuringia = 1; nlp_thuringia = 1;
go-to: mp

WIP


@no_majority_thuringia
title: There is no clear governing majority.
view-if: grand_coalition_thuringia <= 50 and bourgeois_coalition_thuringia <= 50 and right_coalition_thuringia <= 50 and united_left_coalition_thuringia <= 50 and nlp_tl <= 50
on-arrival: nlp_thuringia = 1 if was_nlp_thuringia; in_nlp_majority_thuringia = 1 if was_in_nlp_majority_thuringia; in_united_left_coalition_thuringia = 1 if was_in_united_left_coalition_thuringia; in_grand_coalition_thuringia = 1 if was_in_grand_coalition_thuringia; in_bourgeois_coalition_thuringia = 1 if was_in_bourgeois_coalition_thuringia; in_right_coalition_thuringia = 1 if was_in_right_coalition_thuringia;

There is no path to a majority government for now. The current government will stay in power as a minority coalition.





@mp

